name: Gul Panag
Gul Panag
text: her face devoid of any emotion as she trooped in rhythm with her comrades.  She was older than most others, but her stride - as young and energetic. She also had a story, but one that was different from most others.

name: Gul Panag
text:
The air was filled with festivities and celebrations. Behind the 350 proud lady officers were an equal number of stories - of spirit, of resilience, of valor and of pride. 
One of them who marched in her sparkling whites was Lt. Sandhya Wadhwa..

name: Gul Panag
text: "The cold Delhi winter morning did not seem to mar their spirit. 350 women officers from the Indian Armed Forces marched with gusto, smartly saluting the dignitaries and the then US President Barack Obama who was the guest of honor on India‚Äôs Republic Day celebrations. "

name: Gul Panag
text:
‚ÄúKeep calm and finish the job‚Äù- is what her husband would often say. Sandhya Wadhwa decided to join the Navy to finish her husband Commander Wadhwa‚Äôs unfinished service .

name: Gul Panag
text:

name: Gul Panag
text: When vehicles are scrapped as per industry norms, the rubber, plastic, copper and metal are separated and fluids drained- making all separated material ready for recycling. Significantly increasing production of scrap steel- something we import a lot of.

name: Gul Panag
text: Currently most of the scrapping is done by the disorganised sector - not only making it unsafe for those involved  but also resulting in wastage.

name: Gul Panag
text: For example - an old car at the end of its life pollutes the air 8 times more than a new one; a 15 year old truck pollutes 10 times more than a new one. Such vehicles are also highly unsafe for  as the metal structure of the vehicle is compromised with wear & tear over time.

name: Gul Panag
text:
Most mature auto markets have a well defined scrapping policy. 
A policy like this is a huge step because India has over 25 million ELVs (End of Life vehicles) plying on roads-  with emissions way above the permissable limits .

name: Gul Panag
text: At Cero, India's first organised Vehicle recycler ( an M& M and Government of India Enterprise) vehicles are 'scrapped' systematically and scientifically. A policy that will  determine and define  the 'life' of a vehicle will soon be announced by the Government .

I‚Äôve made a conscious decision to repeat outfits going forward. Remembering the journey of each outfit has its own sweet pleasure.
What are your thoughts on 'repeating outfits' ?

name: Gul Panag
text: Even those who are not in the public gaze. One thing that gets my goat is - ‚Äònot repeating outfits ‚Äò. Why the hell not ? Men can wear that same black suit again and again. But we can‚Äôt . Why ? Who decides? Another random stereotype that has been thrust on women- by women .ü§¶üèª‚Äç‚ôÄÔ∏è

name: Gul Panag
text: As a somewhat recognisable person, there are folks who write about what my kind wears. The pressure to please those faceless well meaning folks ( I like to give them the benefit of good intentions- the people that judge our clothes, appearance, weight , etc) is on everyone.

name: Gul Panag
text:
Specially when it comes to outfits that are for occasional use.
Probably because I‚Äôm lazy. And super busy. And somehow cannot get around to planning ahead when it comes to my sartorial selections. ü§¶üèª‚Äç‚ôÄÔ∏èü§¶üèª‚Äç‚ôÄÔ∏è

name: Gul Panag
text: Bad weather is something that can be forecasted and planned for, to ensure operations are deferred for at least a few hours. Sometimes that's all that is required. Yes, there will be disruptions & delays but not shutdowns, injury and loss of life. @HardeepSPuri @AAI_Official

text:

name: Gul Panag
text: A rethink in the airport decision making process and its chain of command needs to be established that is free of commercial and government pressures when it comes to safety.  @HardeepSPuri @MoCA_GoI  @AAI_Official

name: Gul Panag
text:
A call to shutdown the airport needs to be taken to AVOID accidents not AFTER accidents. This is a process followed in most mature aviation countries in Europe, North America etc. @HardeepSPuri @MoCA_GoI 
We need to start the process of getting there .

text:
